00:58:15.680 --> 00:58:20.180
I don't know why you wouldn't.

00:58:20.180 --> 00:58:26.367
What does it hurt you to give a five-minute altar call, pastors?

00:58:26.367 --> 00:58:29.394
Well, I don't know.

00:58:29.394 --> 00:58:31.380
'Well, I know everybody in here.

00:58:31.380 --> 00:58:32.540
' Five minutes.

00:58:36.405 --> 00:58:36.590
It just takes a couple minutes to give people an opportunity.

00:58:36.590 --> 00:58:54.608
Maybe they're not right with the Lord and you believe you're just expecting them to be right, and you don't ever give them an opportunity to change.

00:58:57.735 --> 00:58:59.623
You don't give them an opportunity to make a choice.

00:58:59.623 --> 00:59:09.413
There are so many mega churches where maybe, you know, one thing about the church where we used to go to, he gave an altar call every single week.

00:59:09.413 --> 00:59:18.564
And I'd go back and count all the people who got saved, and we would get truckloads of people saved.

00:59:18.564 --> 00:59:19.453
Truckloads every week.

00:59:19.453 --> 00:59:24.147
Sometimes we'd get over 150 to 600 in a big revival service or whatever.

00:59:34.720 --> 00:59:34.940
They would come in and we'd bring them in from downtown.

00:59:34.940 --> 00:59:47.560
So, they had a women's ministry that went to the strip clubs and they would talk to the strippers and to the people there, and they would try to get the strippers saved.

00:59:52.480 --> 00:59:56.589
I believe they called it Daughters of Eve or something like that.

00:59:56.589 --> 01:00:05.360
I don't remember, but they were always trying to reach the lost, always trying to get people out of the pit of hell.

01:00:21.440 --> 01:00:21.671
And I respect that about a church.

01:00:21.671 --> 01:00:28.771
I'll support you until the cows come home if you're getting people saved.

01:00:28.771 --> 01:00:30.560
Give people an opportunity to make a choice.

01:00:30.920 --> 01:00:32.869
I remember what it was like to be lost.

01:00:46.640 --> 01:00:46.880
I remember being on the verge.

01:01:01.417 --> 01:01:01.783
If I would have died, I would have gone to hell.

01:01:01.783 --> 01:01:10.776
Living in the world, you think, 'Oh, you know, I'm going to live in sin.

01:01:10.776 --> 01:01:12.889
You're going to do all this stuff.

01:01:12.889 --> 01:01:14.520
I'm just going to make it.

01:01:14.520 --> 01:01:18.960
' No, you have to be separate.

01:01:18.960 --> 01:01:23.900
Now, I'm going to tell you, I know grace covers a multitude of sins.

01:01:34.977 --> 01:01:35.354
I get it.

01:01:35.354 --> 01:01:47.907
But you don't deliberately bathe in sin and say, 'I'm going to live this way and have a good time.

01:01:47.907 --> 01:01:53.960
' Be holy as I am holy, and you try.

01:01:53.960 --> 01:02:06.218
God forgive me, but I believe a real ministry in these last days should be a soul-winning ministry.

01:02:06.218 --> 01:02:22.120
I challenge every person who's watching here: if you have a ministry, if you have a platform to give people an opportunity to accept Jesus Christ as Lord and personal savior, you're going to be held accountable for it.

01:02:48.028 --> 01:02:48.256
I truly believe that you're going to stand before the Lord, and He's going to look at you and say, 'Why did you never give My people a time?

01:02:48.256 --> 01:02:50.733
Why did you never give an opportunity?

01:02:50.733 --> 01:02:52.740
Why did you do that?

01:02:52.740 --> 01:02:54.097
' 'Well, you know what?

01:02:54.097 --> 01:02:55.020
It wasn't popular.

01:02:55.020 --> 01:02:55.900
I was embarrassed.

01:02:56.340 --> 01:02:56.846
I was ashamed.

01:02:56.846 --> 01:03:04.234
' If you're ashamed to speak His name, He won't speak your name before the Father.

01:03:04.234 --> 01:03:15.790
I truly believe it's time for us to become radical and get ready for His coming.

01:03:15.800 --> 01:03:19.150
It's time.

01:03:19.160 --> 01:03:21.560
We have to wake up.

01:03:21.560 --> 01:03:23.149
We're running out of time.

01:03:31.120 --> 01:03:31.369
But yet, there are so many people that act like it's just life as normal.

01:03:31.369 --> 01:03:39.178
They don't even really act like there's anything different.

01:03:39.178 --> 01:03:53.030
All around them, they keep doing the same thing, expecting different results.

01:03:53.040 --> 01:03:57.686
But they don't even try to get people saved.

01:03:57.686 --> 01:03:59.309
They don't care.

01:03:59.309 --> 01:04:19.787
Well, you know, if we had a guest come—I guess we had one person that came to our service that was new—but evangelism is the major way.

01:04:19.787 --> 01:04:23.544
Evangelism is the only way.

01:04:47.225 --> 01:04:47.690
I believe you get the evangelist coming; that's why there's a five-fold ministries.

01:04:53.667 --> 01:04:53.813
The evangelist brings the newcomers in, and the pastor keeps them.

01:05:01.714 --> 01:05:02.000
You know, you have to disciple these people.

01:05:07.160 --> 01:05:07.425
And I'm telling you, they're coming in by the big freightliner loads.

01:05:07.425 --> 01:05:15.086
It's not going to be these little bitty ones, like throwing a pole out and reeling one in.

01:05:15.086 --> 01:05:18.600
I'm talking massive shrimping boats full of people with big old nets.

01:05:18.600 --> 01:05:19.200
They're coming.

01:05:19.200 --> 01:05:20.200
What will you do?

01:05:20.200 --> 01:05:21.170
Will you help Him?

01:05:21.170 --> 01:05:24.480
The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few, ladies and gentlemen.

01:05:24.480 --> 01:05:30.747
He's the Lord of the harvest, and I just want to challenge you all to really wake up.

01:05:37.507 --> 01:05:48.555
And so if I come across critical to YouTubers or to prophetic channels or whatever and say, 'If you're not leading people to Jesus, you're a false prophet,' I say it out of frustration and I apologize to people when I say it.

01:05:57.680 --> 01:05:57.988
I shouldn't come across so rude.

01:05:57.988 --> 01:06:06.325
It doesn't make you a false prophet for not leading people to Jesus; it just makes you lazy.

01:06:06.325 --> 01:06:11.508
It's time to get radical and serious about the Lord.

01:06:11.508 --> 01:06:15.040
But I want to pray tonight.

01:06:15.040 --> 01:06:16.496
Let's pray for the lost.

01:06:16.496 --> 01:06:24.147
Let's pray for whatever He has for us to pray for.

01:06:28.040 --> 01:06:31.040
I am grateful that nothing happened today on St.

01:06:31.040 --> 01:06:32.474
Patrick's Day.

01:06:32.474 --> 01:06:35.653
We had all the parades.

01:06:35.653 --> 01:06:42.440
Everything went off without a hitch, and I don't see that anybody got hurt.

01:06:42.440 --> 01:06:49.480
So, I'm so thankful for that.

01:06:49.480 --> 01:06:55.400
We didn't have any terrorist attacks today.

01:06:55.400 --> 01:06:57.635
There weren't any lone-wolf shooters.

01:06:57.635 --> 01:07:04.529
How many times have we come out of this, and we're victorious every time, right?

01:07:04.529 --> 01:07:25.640
We believe that we will always cover our nation in prayer as praying, believing believers—not begging believers, but believing believers who believe that God is who He says He is and that Psalm 91 is ours.

01:07:32.274 --> 01:07:32.651
No hexes or vexes will come nigh any of us.

01:07:32.651 --> 01:07:34.670
Do you understand that?

01:07:34.670 --> 01:07:43.206
When they send the hexes and the vexes, they fall to our feet, but the devils they sent go back on them.

01:07:43.206 --> 01:07:44.800
Every single one of them.

01:07:44.800 --> 01:07:52.058
The people who believe in witchcraft the most—you cannot curse whom God has blessed.

01:08:05.048 --> 01:08:05.792
A thousand shall fall at my side and ten thousand at our right hand, but nothing shall come nigh me.

01:08:05.792 --> 01:08:10.700
So all the hexes and the vexes, they fall at my feet.

01:08:10.700 --> 01:08:15.286
And the demons that you thought you controlled turn back on you.

01:08:15.286 --> 01:08:18.415
They turn back on you.

01:08:29.697 --> 01:08:32.160
And I pray for you.

01:08:46.008 --> 01:08:46.304
I pray for you because you touch not God's anointed and you do no prophets any harm.

01:08:53.578 --> 01:08:53.907
I truly believe with all my heart He provides protection over His people.

01:08:53.907 --> 01:09:02.612
He said He would give His angels charge over us, and they bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

01:09:02.612 --> 01:09:20.099
So the hexes and the vexes, the satanic wizardry, the witchcraft—all the things that try to come against you—and no, it does not bear fruit in me because of the blood of Jesus.

01:09:25.434 --> 01:09:25.902
We make much of the blood.

01:09:25.902 --> 01:09:28.490
We make much of this covenant.

01:09:28.490 --> 01:09:31.063
We make much of the blood.

01:09:31.063 --> 01:09:40.235
We anoint ourselves with oil, and it makes much of us—the blood that never loses its power.

01:09:53.360 --> 01:09:53.680
We pray for you to get saved.

01:09:53.680 --> 01:09:59.229
We pray for you to turn from your wicked ways.

01:10:01.920 --> 01:10:02.120
The devil has deceived you.

01:10:14.173 --> 01:10:14.431
You believe he'll reward you in his kingdom.

01:10:17.796 --> 01:10:17.968
You believe he'll give you prosperity.

01:10:19.000 --> 01:10:29.800
You believe if you sell your soul to him and drink chicken blood or cat blood or whatever you're doing with the blood of the innocent, it's going to give you more power.

01:10:29.800 --> 01:10:37.320
It's going to give you a coven, and you're going to get to do all these things.

01:10:37.320 --> 01:10:45.413
But the bottom line is, the moment you die, you're going to spend eternity in hell, and he's going to laugh at you.

01:10:45.413 --> 01:10:49.040
He's going to laugh at you because you were so deceived.

01:10:51.032 --> 01:11:03.809
The very spells you cast with hexes and vexes and the things you do—the devils that you sent out come back on you.

01:11:03.809 --> 01:11:10.150
So I don't understand that automatically doesn't show love.

01:11:10.160 --> 01:11:23.480
God is love, and he loves you, and he wants you to turn from your wicked ways.

01:11:23.480 --> 01:11:27.029
He wants you to repent of your sins.

01:11:27.029 --> 01:11:33.820
"Seek first the kingdom, and all these things will be added unto you.

01:11:33.820 --> 01:11:43.320
" The very devil that you think you can control will soon drag your soul to hell.

01:11:43.823 --> 01:11:45.080
You don't control no devil.

01:11:45.080 --> 01:11:46.080
They're playing you.

01:11:47.743 --> 01:11:55.720
And you think every single time that you do these things against Christians, and you try so hard to destroy churches and all this stuff, it gives you a power trip.

01:11:55.720 --> 01:12:00.225
But the very bottom line is the Lord shows me.

01:12:00.225 --> 01:12:04.693
He said, "Brandon, I love every single one of them.

01:12:04.693 --> 01:12:07.497
I died for every single one of them.

01:12:22.425 --> 01:12:22.680
" All those that are practicing occultic witchcraft, voodoo, and sorcery—all these demonic things—he said, "I died for every single one of them.

01:12:22.680 --> 01:12:25.105
I love every single one of them.

01:12:25.105 --> 01:12:27.800
But they're in rebellion towards me.

01:12:27.800 --> 01:12:33.657
" Unless a man is born again, he will not enter into the kingdom of God.

01:12:39.080 --> 01:12:40.462
And the devil is never going to overthrow God.

01:12:59.133 --> 01:12:59.391
The one that created the devil that fell laughs at the devil.

01:12:59.391 --> 01:13:01.347
He laughs at his plans.

01:13:01.347 --> 01:13:02.347
He laughs.

01:13:02.347 --> 01:13:10.173
But he's lied so much to you because it doesn't take character to be a devil.

01:13:10.173 --> 01:13:33.667
All of a sudden, when you surrendered to him and you gave him your soul and all these things happened, he gave you a lot of power really quick because he wants you to kill, steal, and destroy with it.

01:13:33.667 --> 01:13:42.480
But God, it takes you to be refined to lay down your life before him as a living sacrifice.

01:13:46.480 --> 01:13:47.680
"Jesus, I need you.

01:13:47.680 --> 01:13:49.956
I need a savior.

01:13:49.956 --> 01:13:53.920
" But peace that passes all understanding belongs to the believer.

01:14:01.600 --> 01:14:15.738
The torment that you have every night when you go to bed with the demonic spirits that bother you and give you nightmares and the things that try to wrap around your mind—you don't have to live with that.

01:14:15.738 --> 01:14:16.733
Jesus loves you.

01:14:16.733 --> 01:14:18.905
He died for you.

01:14:28.520 --> 01:14:28.775
And I just pray for every single one of you that come against me, and I say, "I pray for you.

01:14:28.775 --> 01:14:35.246
I pray for God to bless you," that you would know him as Lord and personal savior.

01:14:35.246 --> 01:14:41.526
There is a day coming when it will be too late for you.

01:14:41.526 --> 01:14:44.840
There will be a day when you'll take your last breath.

01:15:32.520 --> 01:15:33.380
I heard a nurse say she was in the hospital and she always knows whenever a Christian is in the room.

01:15:33.380 --> 01:16:28.520
She was a hospice nurse, and she said the atmosphere when a believer would die would be all in the atmosphere of the hospital, and there would be so much peace and sometimes even a really sweet fragrance.

01:16:30.240 --> 01:16:54.320
But when somebody that was in the occult dies or somebody was a witch, there was always a sulfur, rotten-egg smell.

01:16:54.320 --> 01:17:17.874
They would sometimes, as they're getting ready to take their last breath, start screaming in agony as the devils were pulling them out of their body and dragging them to hell.

01:17:17.874 --> 01:17:30.053
She said, "As I heard that, I went, 'Oh my God.

01:17:30.053 --> 01:17:47.640
'" You know, they say when Kathryn Kuhlman passed away, she passed away in Tulsa at the heart hospital.

01:17:47.640 --> 01:18:02.020
And they said the whole floor where she was at when she went home filled with the fragrance of roses.

01:18:10.960 --> 01:18:24.800
The presence of the Lord filled the whole floor, and all the nurses and the doctors could smell the sweet fragrance of the Holy Spirit, and it smelled like roses through the whole thing.

01:18:24.800 --> 01:18:30.691
And I thought, "That's somebody that had a relationship with Him.

01:18:33.337 --> 01:18:33.594
That was a friend.

01:18:33.594 --> 01:18:37.490
" Fragrance of roses, fragrance of frankincense and myrrh and beautiful fragrances.

01:18:37.490 --> 01:18:39.680
Follow those that believe.

01:18:39.680 --> 01:18:51.320
When you depart this earth and you give Him your all and you stand before Him—like she always said, "What am I going to do?

01:19:02.800 --> 01:19:02.960
I'm going to stand before Him—not that I love Him, He already knows that—I've given Him my all, but say, 'Jesus, I tried.

01:19:22.230 --> 01:19:22.565
I did the best I could with what You've given me.

01:19:22.565 --> 01:19:26.200
'" That's what I want to do, just like that.

01:19:26.200 --> 01:19:37.091
Not that I want to be a parrot, but I want to be able to say, "Jesus, I tried.

01:19:47.510 --> 01:19:47.765
I led as many people as I could to You.

01:19:50.440 --> 01:19:52.760
I told them about the baptism of the Holy Ghost.

01:20:03.000 --> 01:20:03.396
I told them they didn't have to walk in poverty.

01:20:05.376 --> 01:20:09.093
I told them they could be blessed according to Deuteronomy 28.

01:20:13.693 --> 01:20:20.570
I told them if they give, it shall be given unto them: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, running over.

01:20:20.570 --> 01:20:29.475
I told them they could be healed in their body; Lord, they didn't have to have sickness.

01:20:33.000 --> 01:20:33.427
I tried.

01:20:33.427 --> 01:20:53.364
" But the main thing of all the things that I ever tell you that's coming—I can tell you about Cuba, what the Lord shows me whenever He gives me these things, but I can't control it.

01:20:53.364 --> 01:20:59.604
People go, "Brandon, do you have a word for Australia?

01:20:59.604 --> 01:21:05.578
Do you not have a word for the Philippines?

01:21:19.413 --> 01:21:20.107
You never have this.

01:21:20.800 --> 01:21:21.560
" I don't control it.

01:21:32.227 --> 01:21:32.631
He only shows me what He wants me to see.

01:21:34.496 --> 01:21:35.552
I don't control it.

01:21:37.664 --> 01:21:51.310
I see in part, hear in part, and in that moment is what He has for me.

01:21:51.320 --> 01:21:52.027
Tell my people this.

01:21:52.027 --> 01:21:58.550
Wouldn't it be wonderful if you could just see what you wanted to see, right?

01:22:10.733 --> 01:22:11.236
I guess just look over in Africa: "What's going to happen in Africa?

01:22:11.236 --> 01:22:14.040
" But that's not—then it would be about me.

01:22:39.960 --> 01:22:40.220
It wouldn't be about him; it would have drawn attention to me.

01:22:40.220 --> 01:22:44.960
It wouldn't draw attention to him.

01:22:44.960 --> 01:22:47.725
It's always about deflecting to him.

01:22:47.725 --> 01:22:57.592
If I could control it, if you looked over here at all these investments and things, you'd be richer than Bill Gates.

01:22:57.592 --> 01:23:07.344
But the problem is, this is what destroys you.

01:23:07.344 --> 01:23:16.467
That kind of stuff destroys you if you're not rooted and grounded in him.

01:23:16.467 --> 01:23:27.160
What is it to gain the whole world and to lose your soul?

01:23:27.160 --> 01:23:30.256
That's what the Bible says.

01:23:30.256 --> 01:23:42.017
But I just want you to know there is a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

01:23:42.406 --> 01:23:52.595
And if you're here tonight before we start praying, you tell me, 'Brandon, what you're saying is tugging on my heart.

01:23:58.910 --> 01:23:59.175
I just want Jesus Christ tonight.

01:23:59.175 --> 01:24:02.507
Could you just pray for me?

01:24:02.507 --> 01:24:08.947
' What does it take for God to prove that he loves you?

01:24:08.947 --> 01:24:15.080
He gave his life for you; he died on that cross.

01:24:15.080 --> 01:24:22.264
He suffered greatly for you to walk a victorious life.

01:24:22.264 --> 01:24:27.649
What more does he need to prove to you?

01:24:27.649 --> 01:24:31.144
He says, 'I love you; I died for you.

01:24:31.144 --> 01:24:51.450
' If you were able to see him face to face right now, you would see his hands, and he has massive holes in his hands.

01:25:16.960 --> 01:25:17.280
He has a massive wound in his side.

01:25:18.880 --> 01:25:21.760
He has massive holes in his feet.

01:25:23.160 --> 01:25:27.707
He has scars from the crown of thorns that was upon his head.

01:25:27.707 --> 01:25:36.289
His back took all the stripes, all those lashings, all that for you to walk in victory.

01:25:36.289 --> 01:25:37.825
What more could he give?

01:25:39.200 --> 01:25:42.630
He loves you, and he has a plan for your life.

01:25:42.630 --> 01:25:58.532
So, I just want you to get real with yourself right now and say, 'Brandon, I don't want to live like this anymore.

01:26:12.547 --> 01:26:12.813
I don't want to live bound.

01:26:23.910 --> 01:26:24.380
I don't want to live broke.

01:26:46.720 --> 01:26:47.160
I don't want to live with my marriage in this state.

01:27:00.000 --> 01:27:00.440
I'm tired; I just need a rest.

01:27:00.440 --> 01:27:10.380
' 'Come unto him, all ye that are heavy laden,' and he said he would give you rest.

01:27:10.380 --> 01:27:12.280
Tonight is your night.

01:27:16.057 --> 01:27:16.474
You may be in the occult.

01:27:26.040 --> 01:27:27.440
You may be on here even trying to curse me.

01:27:51.540 --> 01:27:52.140
You may be assigned by Satan himself, being told, 'Go on there, and I want you to try to kill that man.

01:27:52.140 --> 01:27:59.808
' But I pray for you, and I love you.

01:28:07.790 --> 01:28:11.510
I forgive you because I know you're out there; I know you're watching right now.

01:28:11.510 --> 01:28:14.320
But Jesus loves you.

01:28:14.320 --> 01:28:29.587
So I want to give you just this little opportunity to turn away from what you're doing.

01:28:48.640 --> 01:28:48.980
I want you to accept Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

01:28:49.320 --> 01:28:55.457
And the moment you confess him, he'll forgive you.

01:29:05.840 --> 01:29:07.220
I forgive you.

01:29:07.220 --> 01:29:08.600
Tonight's your night.

01:29:08.600 --> 01:29:11.080
Tonight's your night to turn from witchcraft.

01:29:11.080 --> 01:29:13.780
Tonight's your night to turn from voodoo.

01:29:13.780 --> 01:29:14.680
Tonight's your night.

01:29:14.680 --> 01:29:15.480
Jesus loves you.

01:29:15.480 --> 01:29:27.190
But you've got to get real with God and you got to cry out for him.

01:29:29.960 --> 01:29:39.016
And I want you just to get bold about your decision tonight.

01:29:41.320 --> 01:29:45.880
And I want you to put in the comment section right now, 'I need to be saved.

01:29:45.880 --> 01:29:47.000
Tonight's my night.

01:29:47.000 --> 01:29:51.566
' I've been wayward.

01:29:51.566 --> 01:29:55.423
There's some of you that have been wayward.

01:29:55.423 --> 01:30:00.600
Some of you that are running from God with everything you have.

01:30:01.490 --> 01:30:06.343
And you say to me, 'Brandon, I'm not right with the Lord.

01:30:09.070 --> 01:30:09.280
I need help.

01:30:37.120 --> 01:30:37.480
Will you pray for me?

01:30:37.480 --> 01:30:42.773
' And if I'm talking to you, tonight's your night.

01:30:42.773 --> 01:30:45.267
I want to pray for you.

01:30:45.267 --> 01:30:59.525
But I want you to tell us here in a minute, 'Tonight's my night to get saved.

01:30:59.525 --> 01:31:04.040
' I want to turn and make a new decision.

01:31:04.040 --> 01:31:08.875
I want to make a new dedication to Jesus.

01:31:08.875 --> 01:31:19.740
So, I'm going to say a simple prayer for you, and I want you to repeat it after me.

01:31:19.740 --> 01:31:23.855
Say, 'Jesus, I believe you're the Son of God.

01:31:23.855 --> 01:31:29.680
I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.

